name: Zephyry
description: ★★★★★★ - Chronos, the guardian of time, bears a clock on their chest that controls the temporal flow. Elegant and enigmatic, they possess the wisdom of a thousand lives.

name: Captain Morgan
description: ★★★★★★ - Fearless pirate, sails the seas with their loyal parrot, Zephyr. Together, they uncover treasures and face dangers in the ocean depths.

name: Jinxy
description: ★★★★★★ - Agile adventurer, wears a monkey costume that grants incredible dexterity. With quick jumps and precise movements, they explore every corner of the world.

name: Rylan
description: ★★★★★★ - A space explorer wears an astronaut suit with a helmet filled with water and a fish swimming inside, combining science and nature in their intergalactic journey.

name: Pixel Blip
description: ★★★★★★ - An adorable character with a TV on their head displays cute images, charming everyone with animated expressions and spreading joy wherever they go.

name: Journey's Beginning.
description: Thank you for playing Pupa. Exclusive skin that only the first players obtained at launch.
